    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pendants, brooches, or any other jewelry that has as a primary focus a devotional or religious subject or theme. Devotional jewelry has been common since ancient times, and is known in many religions, including Hinduism and Christianity. Wearing of devotional jewelry may be thought to convey blessings, health, or good luck.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
